description: Adventure anime cartoon "Spirited Away" tells the story of a ten-year-old girl named Chihiro Ogino, who, by the will of fate, was destined to find herself in the world of ghosts and monsters. While moving to a new place of residence, Chihiro and his parents find themselves in a deserted town. In one of the empty buildings, there is a restaurant in which the tables are simply bursting with various food. The girl's parents decide to taste the goodies, and after a while they turn into pigs. As it soon turns out, the family was held captive by an evil witch, the ruler of the world of gods and spirits. Now Chihiro has to find a way to disenchant his parents, and most importantly, how to get out of the kingdom of ghosts.
